      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Commercial CFD solver must have documented V&V test suite and version-controlled release process with regression testing.",
      "rationale": "The commercial solver has a documented V&V test suite for internal flows, but the specific hemolysis scalar transport module lacks independent regression testing at the current release version. SQA documentation is available but incomplete for the user-defined hemolysis damage accumulation subroutine."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
