      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Method of manufactured solutions or equivalent benchmark must confirm expected convergence order for all governing equations used in the simulation.",
      "rationale": "MMS verification confirms second-order convergence for momentum and continuity equations. The hemolysis power-law scalar transport equation was verified against an analytical solution for simple Couette flow only; verification in complex rotating geometries was not performed."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
